{
  "texts": [
    "This section describes the models, datasets, training methods, and evaluation metrics in PRBench.",
    "The models under evaluation spans 3 types of architectures: (1) plain CNNs; (2) residual CNNs; and",
    "(3) transformer-based models.",
    "We train a diverse set of models, including VGG-19, SimpleCNN, ResNet-18, ResNet-34, WRN-28-10, ViT (Small/Base/Large), and DeiT (Tiny/Small).",
    "In total, 222 models are trained on 7 datasets: MNIST, SVHN, CIFAR-10, CIFAR-100, CINIC-10, TinyImageNet, and ImageNet-50."
  ]
}